        <mxCell id="t5QTQC3ebWH6XtvLZvS4-4" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;" value="The app will be acted as the run game&lt;div&gt;and also game monitor (service) this will monitor the current screen (foreground) but will not monitor background (as we don&#39;t need powerful mode when game on background)&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
