        <mxCell id="t5QTQC3ebWH6XtvLZvS4-7" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;" value="&lt;div&gt;- Run Game (And play the animation overlay)&lt;/div&gt;- Clear Background Apps&lt;div&gt;- Clear cache (echo 3 &amp;gt; /proc/sys/vm/drop_caches)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- Show toast &quot;Ready to game [How many cleared] Mb Cleared&quot;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;- Execute mode according user define (Awaken, Balanced, Powersave)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- Start Monitoring For Game&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="160" width="290" x="169.97" y="630" as="geometry" />
